stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 730.00 Td (8. MAX10 MIPI Power Fix) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 700.00 Td (Symptom) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 674.00 Td (Holoscan applications reached the FPGA/HSB, but camera configuration failed with I2C transaction errors:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 650.00 Td (hololink._hololink.TransactionError: i2c_transaction i2c_address=0x37) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 640.00 Td (hololink._hololink.TransactionError: i2c_transaction i2c_address=0x1a) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 618.00 Td (Root Cause) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 592.00 Td (Early production MDK boards, both Group A and Group B, shipped with a bug in the MAX10 image. The buggy) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 580.00 Td (  MAX10 image does not apply power to the MIPI connectors. Without MIPI connector power, camera I2C) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 568.00 Td (  communication is impossible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 544.00 Td (Customer release production boards are expected to ship with a fixed MAX10 image and should be plug-and-) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 532.00 Td (  play. Currently available early boards may need MAX10 reflashing.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 508.00 Td (Fix Applied) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 482.00 Td (1. Switch MAX10 onto the JTAG chain by setting SW4 on the carrier board to ON. This is the single switch) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 470.00 Td (  nearest the HDMI connector.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 458.00 Td (2. Use Quartus Programmer GUI to reflash MAX10 with:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 434.00 Td (   max10_top_rtl_v1p1p6_fw_v2p0p1.pof) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 412.00 Td (3. Power off the board.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 400.00 Td (4. Set SW4 back to OFF so the FPGA appears on the JTAG chain again.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 376.00 Td (After this MAX10 update, camera I2C configuration succeeded.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 352.00 Td (Additional Note) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 326.00 Td (Initial production MDK batches may have a carrier micro USB hub that is susceptible to ESD. If the) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 314.00 Td (  carrier micro USB is not detected, for example Windows fails to read descriptors, use the standard JTAG) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 302.00 Td (  connector and a Byte Blaster.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 278.00 Td (------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 254.00 Td (9. AI Demo Examples) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 224.00 Td (YOLOv8 Body Pose) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 198.00 Td (Inside container:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 174.00 Td (apt-get update && apt-get install -y ffmpeg) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 164.00 Td (pip3 install ultralytics onnx) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 144.00 Td (cd examples) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 134.00 Td (yolo export model=yolov8n-pose.pt format=onnx) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 124.00 Td (trtexec --onnx=yolov8n-pose.onnx --saveEngine=yolov8n-pose.engine.fp32) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 114.00 Td (cd -) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 92.00 Td (Run:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 68.00 Td (python3 examples/linux_body_pose_estimation_agx5.py --cam 0 --lines 1080 --frame-rate 30) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 498 28 Td (Page 5 of 7) Tj ET
endstream
