BT /F2 11 Tf 54 730.00 Td (TAO PeopleNet) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 704.00 Td (Download model:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 680.00 Td (curl -L 'https://api.ngc.nvidia.com/v2/models/org/nvidia/team/tao/peoplenet/pruned_quantized_decrypted_v2) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 670.00 Td (.3.3/files?redirect=true&path=resnet34_peoplenet_int8.onnx' -o examples/resnet34_peoplenet_int8.onnx) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 648.00 Td (Run:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 624.00 Td (python3 examples/linux_tao_peoplenet_agx5.py --cam 0 --lines 1080 --frame-rate 30) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 602.00 Td (First run builds a TensorRT engine and can take several minutes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 578.00 Td (If the PeopleNet AGX5 example crashes in InferenceOp, disable metadata in) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 566.00 Td (  examples/linux_tao_peoplenet_agx5.py:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 542.00 Td (self.is_metadata_enabled = False) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 520.00 Td (------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 496.00 Td (10. Display and Runtime Notes) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 466.00 Td (If Holoviz/GLFW fails:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 442.00 Td (Failed to initialize glfw) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 432.00 Td (Authorization required, but no authorization protocol specified) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 422.00 Td (XDG_RUNTIME_DIR is invalid or not set) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 400.00 Td (Run on Thor host before starting Docker:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 376.00 Td (xhost +local:root) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 366.00 Td (xhost +local:docker) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 356.00 Td (xhost +) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 334.00 Td (Inside Docker:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 310.00 Td (export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR=/tmp/runtime-root) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 300.00 Td (mkdir -p $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 290.00 Td (chmod 700 $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 268.00 Td (For receiver buffer warnings:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 244.00 Td (echo 10420224 | sudo tee /proc/sys/net/core/rmem_max) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 222.00 Td (Inside the container as root, omit sudo:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 198.00 Td (echo 10420224 > /proc/sys/net/core/rmem_max) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 176.00 Td (Use Ctrl+C to stop demos. Avoid Ctrl+Z, which suspends jobs and can leave resources open.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 152.00 Td (------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 128.00 Td (11. Known Issues and Lessons Learned) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 98.00 Td (- Thor defaults to 10GbE mode.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 86.00 Td (- 25GbE FPGA images need Thor booted in 25GbE mode.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 74.00 Td (- 10G/25G mode switching requires boot slot / capsule handling, not nmcli.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 62.00 Td (- Early MDK boards may need MAX10 reflashing to power MIPI connectors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 498 28 Td (Page 6 of 7) Tj ET
endstream
