stream
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 742.00 Td (- Camera I2C errors can be caused by missing MIPI connector power, not only cable orientation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 730.00 Td (- hololink-enumerate confirms the FPGA/HSB network path.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 718.00 Td (- GUI failures are often X11 authorization issues.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 706.00 Td (- .sof FPGA programming is volatile; reprogram after FPGA board power cycle.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 694.00 Td (- For customer demos on AGX Thor, 10GbE and Linux socket mode are the most stable paths. 25GbE CoE is) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.3 Tf 54 682.00 Td (  available but may show stability issues under some multi-stream scenarios.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 498 28 Td (Page 7 of 7) Tj ET
endstream
